blueprint/src/chapters/AbelJacobi.tex:28:  Functorially, it is the morphism in the category of $k$-schemes induced by the line bundle $\mathcal O_{C \times C}(\Delta - p_1^* P)$ on $C \times C$ via the universal property of $\Pic^0_{C/k}$ as the moduli space of degree-$0$ line bundles on $C$. The Lean formalisation does not follow this route: the Pic-scheme representability machinery (Route~A of the proof of Theorem~\ref{thm:nonempty_jacobianWitness}, in particular sub-step~A.2) is not currently available in Mathlib. See Layer~I of Chapter~\ref{chap:Jacobian} for the formalisation route actually taken.
